text: Walter Hollmann (27 December 1915 - 5 September 1967) was a Czech alpine skier. He competed in the men's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:1967 deaths Category:Czech male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
